    <p>So Banda managed to call home for updates huh? I was hoping that would happen. Some of those jobs and skills will probably help a lot. IIRC he didn’t get Dream Guider till after Banda split off, so Banda should only be getting access to that ability now. Not to mention Demiurge. That signature mix of utterly abnormal and perfectly normal is very Van. Hiroshi took it pretty well though. I’m now looking forward to the day when the Amemiyas realize both their kids are friends with an eldritch abomination… I was wondering what happened to Super Mana Recovery. I<span id="wpdiscuz-readmore-16669_0"><span class="wpdiscuz-hellip">… </span><span class="wpdiscuz-readmore" title="Read more »">Read more »</span></span></p>
