    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>While I agree it is not a perfect form of Magic, as it is the purest form of Magic it does have advantages. Remember Asagi’s ability lets him stop all magic in a radius around him. However, as he learned the hard way No-Attribute Magic still worked inside his cheat ability. It has its downsides like Mana Bullet being a point blank attack, unless you can dump like 10k mana into it. I get the impression at least for the time they won’t be able to detect No-Attribute Magic, until they tweak their detection devices or abilities. After all it<span id="wpdiscuz-readmore-16794_16761"><span class="wpdiscuz-hellip">… </span><span class="wpdiscuz-readmore" title="Read more »">Read more »</span></span></p>
</div>
    <div class="wpd-comment-footer">
    <div class="wpd-vote">
    <div class="wpd-vote-up wpd_not_clicked">
