    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>One Banda’s trash is another brat’s treasure! </p>
<p>Curious as to how the connection was made? </p>
<p>It feels so satisfying when Rikudou and Rodidiot experience frustrations. Those artificial spirits were pretty pathetic by Lamda standards.</p>
<p>Amemiyas are a little disappointing …c’mon, suspect your fellow Bravers more! What happened to Narumi’s unease with Rikudou? Gotta admire Shaman a little …he had enough sense not to tackle Banda …not that that sense will last.</p>

