</div>
    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>It was already clear enough that the point was incredibly poorly presented, because it’s not as easy to make an inference about insect sized living beings possessing sentience and intelligence as opposed to beings that walk upright, look like humans except with a different skin tone, use a spoken language that humans can understand and use tools and clothing.It is nonsensical to assume the former to possess sentience, but it is very reasonable to assume such a thing about the latter. It makes it a poor comparison that does nothing to illustrate the point.</p>

</div>
