    <p>Don’t get me wrong, his preaching helped the “human-like” races of vida a little in getting employment, the Dark elves , the Titans and beast kin, but only the lowest of positions though, nothing to really improve their overall lifestyle or social standing or even give a bright future for them, that’s something that even an ordinary citizen can see 🙈, in the grand scheme of things at beast they would be second class citizens without the rights that come with it but hey at least they won’t be killed? 🤷🏾‍♂️</p>

