    <blockquote><p>He is now the most godlike MC I know.</p><p></p><p></p><p> He can now grant power? This is godhood if I ever seen any in a light novel/manga/anime.</p></blockquote>
<p>Van wouldn’t be happy to hear you say that.<br/>
 </p><div class="wpdiscuz-spoiler-wrap"><div class="wpdiscuz-spoiler wpdiscuz-spoiler-closed"><i class="fas fa-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i>Title</div><div class="wpdiscuz-spoiler-content"> “Self-proclaimed human”<br/>
Because no matter how obvious divinity he obtains, he insists he’s just a human (as in a mortal being, not racially).  He has an ever-growing complex about this.  And getting that title only stung him further.</div></div><p></p>

