    <p>Banda can use his Active skills.  That’s how he can affect the material world the skill Materialize.  He also gets the passive bonuses that’s why he so outclassed the kidnappers.  </p>
<p>Origin admittedly doesn’t have the skill system, but Banda kept all the benefits of it.  I think the reason is because Banda is an off shoot of Van.  So Banda can’t really increase the skills levels, but he can benefit from Vans efforts.</p>

