    <p>Yes, like we saw him using Venom Secretion to take care of the maids, which is definitely not something he can do without skills. The difference between Passive and Active skills is just whether the system thinks it is an automatic thing versus something you think about doing (i.e. difference between heart beating and moving your arm).</p>

