    <p>“Ah, I’ve gone and woken you up, Meh-kun. Here, wriggle-wriggle,” said Banda, extending a tentacle of the Demon King towards her.<br/>
“Wriggle-wriggle!” Mei giggled happily.<br/>
Banda kept her entertained until she fell asleep once more.</p>
<p>I’m just telling you, this scene will bring serious consequences, Listen, it will bring consequences</p>

