×××××××<br/>
Mei: So you are approaching me? Instead of running away, you are approaching this Mei-sama?<br/>
Amemiya Hiroto: I can’t preach my useless ideologies without approaching you after all!<br/>
Mei: Then come closer as your wish!<br/>
××××××××<br/>
 Banda(monotone voice):MUDA! MUDA! MUDA! MUDA! MUDA! MUDA! MUDA!</p>

