    <div class="wpd-comment-text">
    <p>It’s still a cheat so even if degraded, it should still be more than enough mana regen for any mage in Origin. Also some cheats can be improved with training even in Origin. Doug’s Hecatoncheir was a cheat that didn’t have fine control originally but he trained and improved it in Origin to be able to do precise tasks with it like knitting. Hiroshi could possible train to improve his mana regen cheat to either regen mana faster or regen more at once thus making it effectively an infinite mana source.</p>

