    <p>Well he IS dreaming tho , yeah it’s a lucid dream but IT is still a dream from his POV, the fact he didn’t immediately stuff the “Thing” into his mouth is enough self awareness that a child his age wouldn’t normally have, in  a dream for that matter.</p>
